	Press, 2008, pp. 59-71.</i> 
	<li>Read: <a href="https://www.redalyc.org/journal/5117/511767145003/511767145003.pdf"
	target="blank">Einstein and Nazi physics: When science meets
	ideology and prejudice</a>, <i>Me&#768tode Science Studies Journal</i>, 10(2020):147-155 by <a href="https://www.philipball.co.uk/" 
	target="blank">Philip Ball</a>. </li>  
	<!--<li>Read:
	<a href="https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/how-2-pro-nazi-nobelists-attacked-einstein-s-jewish-science-excerpt1/#"
